subtitle: 4/20 Fits
content: Dress in the latest high fashion — log in and play GTA Online this week to receive the Gold 420 Pendant, Green 420 Festival Outfit and Yeti Earth Day Hoodie. Round out your 4/20 collection by completing any Biker Business Sell Mission this week to receive the Güffy Drug Rug Hoodie.
